<p><b>What is QA in call center?</b> Call center quality assurance is the process of monitoring and analyzing your service team's customer conversations. QA and team leads use QA software to easily assess these conversations against quality criteria. This ensures your teams are achieving their goals and your customers' expectations.</p>
